title: LINK : fatal error LNK1181

labels.name: A-linkage
labels.description: Area: linking into static, shared libraries and binaries

body:
i use rust 
```
#[link(name = "testlib")]
extern {
    fn  hello();
}
```
then get error 

>   = note:  LINK : fatal error LNK1181: cannot open input file testlib.lib

build.rs
```
fn main() {
    println!(r"cargo:rustc-link-search=D:\project\c\testlib\build");
}

```
i have installed vs 2019.and spent  a lot of time to find a solution.

rustup show

```
active toolchain
----------------

stable-x86_64-pc-windows-msvc (default)
rustc 1.39.0 (4560ea788 2019-11-04)
```
